flowchart TD
    Start([User launches App]) --> GetConfig[Get Application Config Directory]
    GetConfig --> EnsureDir[Create Directory if needed]
    EnsureDir --> CheckSocket{Does socket file exist?}

    CheckSocket -- Yes --> TryConnect[Connect to Unix socket]
    TryConnect --> ConnectSuccess{Connection successful?}

    ConnectSuccess -- Yes --> SendArgs[JSON encode args & write to socket]
    SendArgs --> Exit0([Exit App code 0])

    ConnectSuccess -- No (Dead Socket) --> DeleteDead[Delete dead socket file]
    DeleteDead --> CreateSocket[Create new Unix ServerSocket]

    CheckSocket -- No --> CreateSocket

    CreateSocket --> SocketSuccess{Socket created successfully?}

    SocketSuccess -- No --> ErrorMode{Check errorMode flag}
    ErrorMode -- exit --> ExitMinus1([Exit App code -1])
    ErrorMode -- throwError --> ThrowEx([Throw Exception])
    ErrorMode -- returnFalse --> RetFalse([Return False to main])
    ErrorMode -- returnTrue --> RetTrue([Return True to main])

    SocketSuccess -- Yes --> Listen[Listen for incoming connections]
    Listen --> RetTrue

    %% Second instance connections coming into the listening socket
    Listen -- On Connection Event --> ReadStream[Read byte stream]
    ReadStream --> UTF8[UTF-8 decode stream]
    UTF8 --> JSONDecode[JSON decode arguments string]
    JSONDecode --> CmdProcessor[Pass decoded list to cmdProcessor]
    CmdProcessor --> ProcessDone([Handle Args in App])
